page_content: The page contains archived videos related to various events and activities in the Kanton Thurgau for the year 2016.
The page offers a course focusing on art and social sciences, targeting students from 5th to 7th grade.
The page provides a downloadable PDF guide for tax-related information for the year 2016.
The page describes a work assignment event for A-classes aimed at holistic assessment of students' physical, psychological, and social skills.
The page provides information on the vocational training for bakers, confectioners, and pastry chefs, focusing on the skills and tasks involved.
The page describes a workshop for teenagers on creating social media video clips, including tips on internet safety.
The page provides resources for school libraries, including information on a library management software called NetBiblio.
